      "span_text": "Herbicide-resistant wild-oat populations M3/4, M3/5, M3/27 (A. fatua) and M5W/7 (A. sterilis), hereinafter called R1, R2, R3 and R4, respectively (Ahmad-Hamdani et al., 2011), were used in this study along with a susceptible A. fatua population"
